Package: com.yourhandle.liquidglass
Name: LiquidGlass
Version: 1.3.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm
Description: [EXPERIMENTAL] Gives iOS UI elements a real-time Metal-rendered Liquid Glass look.
 - App Library icons and folders use a high-performance renderer based on winaviation's work (thanks to WinsAviation)
 - Home Screen folder icons retain the original effect
 - Quick action toggles and passcode buttons are glassed
 - Notifications on the Home Screen are also glass
 - Dock, switches, and sliders use LiquidGlassKit
 - For iOS 14-18, rootful, rootless, and roothide supported
Maintainer: Your Name <you@example.com>
Author: Your Name <you@example.com>
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate | substitute | libhooker | ellekit, preferenceloader
